Simple HTML for these demos. The layout for editor.js is done with blueprint CSS 
framework, but nothing in the JS depends on it. 

    <script src="/js_demos/images.js"></script>
    <div>Drag images into the box:</div>
    <div id="list"></div>


    <script src="/js_demos/editor.js"></script>
